"Eww.. so ugly!"
This quote has been said by uncountable number of people. People judge each other by their looks. Until this moment, I still don't understand in what kind of standard makes someone considered "ugly". Because I personally think, this is sad and STUPID at the same time. People refer someone's face to be called "ugly". And yet a person's face is something that he/she didn't choose to have, something innate. Making fun of someone's face by calling them "ugly" is just like making fun of someone's name, race, religion, etc. Thus, making it hurtful for the victims since they were born with their faces and don't even know how to change them, leading to anxiety, depression, and ofc suicide. The word "ugly" itself is one of the most "lethal" words there is. It only takes one person to call someone "ugly" to make him/her live his life miserably. "You're ugly" is just equivalent to "Just KILL YOURSELF". Therefore, please respect each other's appearance. Everybody's beautiful as human beings, male or female, everyone's equal. And no, I'm no homo lol
Sorry for my bad english. Just wanna defend beautiful "ugly" people
.
.
.
